				<td colspan="2"><span>Everything that applies to ae kiting applies equally if not moreso to earthshaker aeing by warriors.  Warriors can kill 100+ mobs at a time, especially using the callers.  It creates tremendous server lag, sometimes up to a minute if there are lots of mobs.  It uses up content others could be using.  It is the best xp in the game, hands down, beating the current form of ae kiting that is being nerfed.
<br />

<br />
It may be more rare, but for a high level bard, every argument they make against ae kiting, which IMO was fun now and again, applies to earthshaker ae.</span></td>
