				<td colspan="2"><span>For those who don't know, putting shaman slow on an warrior with earthshaker makes it swing ~2x per minute.  That makes it proc every 1 to 2 swings, depending on aa and dex.  If a war in this situation hits rampage next to a big group of mobs, it procs 1 or 2 times for every 2 mobs.  100 mobs in range = 70+ procs instantly, which makes for 90+ dead mobs in one tick, depending on resists and the mobs hit points.  Caller in Luclin is a favorite place for this.</span></td>
