				<td class="PanelBodyAlternate"><span class="SmallBoldText">Re: So where is the Earthshaker nerf?<a name="61337"/></span><br><span class="SmallText"> Posted: </span><span class="SmallText">Sep 10 04 1:17 PM</span></td>
			</tr><tr>
				<td colspan="2"><span>100 mobs + AE rampage so warrior hits/ has a chance to hit each of those 100 mobs.  He's slowed with a weapon that swings 1c per minute or so and the Proc Per minute means that basically that first swing he's gonna get a proc.
<br />

<br />
so in one swing he swings at all those mobs with a *gauranteed* proc on each of the mobs he is swinging on.
<br />

<br />
The earth shaker proc is an AE proc for 175? points of damage.  If it procs on 100 mobs and each mob gets hit for the 175, in addition it's an AE proc so every mob gets hit with the AE proc from every other single mob's individual proc.
<br />

